1468.name: SA Nicro 602 CA (6025HT) strip
1468.Applications: Electro slag cladding jobs that have to resist extreme high temperature and for cladding steels or stainless steels to obtain a high temperature resistant surface against oxidation.
1468.Suitable_For: Cladding against high temperature, radiant heater tubes, furnace rolls, muffles in bright annealing furnaces (H2 atmosphere), rotary kilns, waste gas components, hydrogen production, methanol and ammonia synthesis, 2.4633, NiCr25FeAlY, Nicrofer 6025 HT.
